latestIgtvVideos.title: RECREATING ALL 6 CHARACTERS FROM F.R.I.E.N.D.S 💫
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Friends- tv show is the best series I've ever watched and will remain at the top of my favorites list because it is the perfect blend of drama,romance,comedy etc to lighten things up. It also has some good life lessons and some sad bits. I mean, its a type of show that you would like to re-watch over and over without getting bored unlike other shows where you get bored. 

So I had to recreate all of these beauties and make a video out of it. I tried my best to recreate their outfits as close as possible. 
I was planning this video from a long time,yk, arranging the outfits,planning how should I go about the editing,how to make it more interesting and appealing to the viewers etc. 

I've put in a lot of effort and mind into this video which I hope you all can make out🙈 This is probably my best and favourite video till now. 
I would definitely like to know your thoughts and suggestions as well,so lmk in the comments❤️

Fun fact: I borrowed 4 of my brother's clothes for this video which really looked like I was wearing a gown back then but I managed somehow.🤪

song: I'll be there for you by @the_rembrandts

To all the creators out there,I know it’s more than a 9 to 5 job with no days off!❤️ Most creators(unless they’ve grown immensely) do it all by themselves! Even the successful ones today started off with managing every role by themselves. 

From content research,script writing,modelling,filming,editing and managing our social media,we wear every hat and I know it can be very overwhelming at days,especially when you’re trying to be consistent on a platform where views can be very inconsistent. 

But I want you all to keep hustling and don’t let this stop you! Even the smallest step taken towards progress is a big step.(khud ko bhi same gyan deti hu roz heheh🥹) 

Tag your creator friend and appreciate them today! ❤️
